{com}. do "/var/folders/p4/tpy5_7mn71sbyj0zqp9zpb5c0000gn/T//SD80414.000000"
{txt}
{com}.         ** Compute per capita gap for each household
.         gen PCGap= MEB - PCExp_ECMEN if PCExp_ECMEN<MEB // the gap is defined only for hh with economic capacity below the MEB
{txt}(267 missing values generated)

{com}.         label var PCGap"Gap, per capita, monthly"
{txt}
{com}. 
{txt}end of do-file

{com}. do "/var/folders/p4/tpy5_7mn71sbyj0zqp9zpb5c0000gn/T//SD80414.000000"
{txt}
{com}.         sum PCGap if Gap_ref==1 // compute average

