{hline 13}{c +}{hline 57}
{space 7}PCGap {c |}{res}        497    8308.338    4066.742   107.6445      20418
{txt}
{com}.         gen PCGap_avg = `r(mean)' if Gap_ref==1 // store calculated average into a variable (defined only for the cohort)
{txt}(518 missing values generated)

