{txt}
{com}.         ** Create a variable representing the different categories of household size
.         recode hhsize (1/3=1) (4/6=2) (7/9=3) (nonmissing=4), gen(hhsize_cat)
{txt}(1,010 differences between {bf:hhsize} and {bf:hhsize_cat})

{com}.         label var hhsize_cat "Classes of household size"
{txt}
{com}.         label define hhsize 1 "Small" 2"Medium" 3"Large" 4"Extra large"
{txt}
{com}.         label val hhsize_cat hhsize
{txt}
{com}.         order hhsize_cat, after(hhsize)
{txt}
{com}. 
{txt}end of do-file

