{com}. do "/var/folders/p4/tpy5_7mn71sbyj0zqp9zpb5c0000gn/T//SD80414.000000"
{txt}
{com}.         ** Create a variable taking the average gap value for each household size category
.         gen PCGap_avg_hhcat = .
{txt}(1,015 missing values generated)

{com}.         label var PCGap_avg_hhcat "Average per capita gap per hh size (cohort: below MEB and food insecure)"
{txt}
{com}. 
.         ** Compute the average gap for household size cat and save into the variable created before
.         forvalues i = 1/4 {c -(} // we will loop through the four household size categories
{txt}  2{com}.         sum  PCGap if Gap_ref==1  & hhsize_cat==`i' // compute average for hh size cat within the gap analysis cohort
{txt}  3{com}.         replace PCGap_avg_hhcat = `r(mean)' if Gap_ref==1 & hhsize_cat==`i' // store average into variable
{txt}  4{com}.         {c )-}

